==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overstock
<hw>O`ver*stock"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Overstocked</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Overstocking</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To fill too full; to supply
in excess; <as>as, to <ex>overstock</ex> a market with goods, or a farm
with cattle</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

